# happygymstats deploy privilege boundary
#
# Permanent (steady-state deploy): release activation + service restart/status.
# Bootstrap-only (one-time setup): install/validate sudoers + install/enable/start adminpanel service.
# Keep entries command-specific; no shell escapes or wildcard service names.

# --- steady-state deploy permissions ---
